history.content: Depends on what grade you want. Usually doing well in a class requires you to understand more than just what is presented in lecture. The fact that there's a final project means you need to understand way more than what is in lecture. Although it's rare to get below A on a graduate class, so if you're just looking to pass then you probably won't need to understand everything in lecture.
